headline: Equinor Strikes Gas in Norwegian Sea's Mistral Sor Well
summary: EQNR and partners find up to 44M barrels of recoverable gas and condensate in the Mistral Sor well, reinforcing Norway's role in Europe's energy security.

headline: ExxonMobil Secures LNG Export Extension for Golden Pass Project
summary: The U.S. Department of Energy grants an extension for XOM's Golden Pass LNG, giving more time to begin exports from the $10B Texas project.
